---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Writing Collective" 
  description="Join our writing collective and share your stories"
>
  <article class="collective">
    <h1>Writing Collective</h1>
    
    <div class="collective-content">
      <p>
        Welcome to our writing collective! This is a space where writers come together to share their stories, 
        support each other, and grow as artists. Whether you're a seasoned writer or just starting out, 
        you're welcome here.
      </p>

      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Share and discuss our writing</li>
        <li>Provide constructive feedback</li>
        <li>Collaborate on projects</li>
        <li>Learn from each other</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How to Join</h2>
      <p>
        To join our collective, simply reach out to us through our contact form or social media channels. 
        We're always looking for new voices and perspectives to add to our community.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .collective {
    max-width: var(--content-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .collective-content {
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .collective-content p {
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .collective-content ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .collective-content ul li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .collective-content ul li::before {
    content: 'üçì';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
  }
</style> 